&lt;p class=&quot;font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal leading-[1.7]&quot;&gt;We&#39;re looking for a &lt;strong&gt;People Operations Specialist&lt;/strong&gt; to join our growing HR team. In this role, you&#39;ll be a go-to resource for employees and a key operator behind the scenes — supporting everything from benefits administration and Workday (HRIS) to onboarding, compliance, and HR policy. You&#39;ll bring structure and care to the day-to-day work that keeps our people programs running smoothly, while also looking for ways to improve and automate how we work.&lt;/p&gt;
