&lt;p&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;auto&quot;&gt;The Senior Data Analyst demonstrates analytical thinking and creative problem solving for business questions across the organization.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;auto&quot;&gt;Working closely with the Senior Manager, Data Analytics, this role serves as a senior business partner to leaders across the company — owning analytics engagements end-to-end, contributing to team planning, and helping shape how Suvoda adopts AI in analytics.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;auto&quot;&gt;Our goal is to build a strong data culture at Suvoda using the strategy of the Data Analytics Cycle. Success will derive from developing new BI solutions, leading AI-enabled analytics pilots, and automating ad-hoc analysis for clear, action-oriented, evolving insights that inform Suvoda’s strategy.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-props=&quot;{}&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;auto&quot;&gt;Responsibilities:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-props=&quot;{}&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;auto&quot;&gt;Own analytics engagements with cross-functional stakeholders end-to-end — from requirements gathering through delivery and adoption — for new and&amp;nbsp;improved BI&amp;nbsp;solutions.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-props=&quot;{}&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;auto&quot;&gt;Develop, test,&amp;nbsp;publish, and&amp;nbsp;maintain&amp;nbsp;Power BI reports and dashboards using data from multiple sources (Snowflake,&amp;nbsp;Web (API), etc.).&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-props=&quot;{}&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
